text: Harlan County is a county in Kentucky. As of the 2020 census, the population was 26,831. Its county seat is Harlan. ==Communities== ===Cities=== * Benham * Cumberland * Evarts * Harlan (county seat) * Loyall * Lynch * Wallins Creek ==References== Category:1810s establishments in Kentucky Category:1819 establishments in Kentucky
title: Harlan County, Kentucky
